1
00:01:26,770 --> 00:01:30,770
=My Dear Guardian=

2
00:01:31,340 --> 00:01:34,120
=Episode 15=

3
00:01:34,821 --> 00:01:36,131
-Hi, Dr. Zhang.
-Hi.

4
00:01:36,266 --> 00:01:37,134
Zhang Yi Chi.

5
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:40,842
It's durian cheese roll.
I bought it from Joy Bakery.

6
00:01:40,883 --> 00:01:42,040
Try it and see
if the taste is still the same.

7
00:01:46,431 --> 00:01:48,120
Thanks for helping out the foundation.

8
00:01:48,507 --> 00:01:50,680
When the application is approved,
I'll treat you to a nice meal.

9
00:02:25,786 --> 00:02:26,655
Xia Chu.

10
00:02:27,541 --> 00:02:28,520
Dr. Zhang, please take a seat.

11
00:02:34,700 --> 00:02:38,120
Which one do you think is tastier?

12
00:02:39,179 --> 00:02:40,080
Let me try it.

13
00:02:40,869 --> 00:02:41,739
No need.

14
00:02:41,812 --> 00:02:43,040
Just take a guess.

15
00:02:46,469 --> 00:02:48,480
Judging from the look,

16
00:02:48,521 --> 00:02:51,000
durian cheese roll
is more appetizing.

17
00:02:51,438 --> 00:02:53,518
However, no doubt
the combination of durian and cheese...

18
00:02:53,559 --> 00:02:56,165
is going to take your breath away
at the first bite.

19
00:02:56,206 --> 00:02:58,146
However, after some time,
you'll get bored of the taste.

20
00:02:59,092 --> 00:03:00,560
Steamed cake is different.

21
00:03:01,038 --> 00:03:03,260
No doubt it is not delicate,

22
00:03:03,301 --> 00:03:06,668
but it has a light taste
and the chewiness is on point.

23
00:03:06,709 --> 00:03:08,879
Many restaurants serve it
as a main course.

24
00:03:09,186 --> 00:03:11,577
Hence,
in comparison to durian cheese roll,

25
00:03:11,618 --> 00:03:13,360
steamed cake is more practical.

26
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,599
The chewiness is on point?

27
00:03:16,299 --> 00:03:19,160
It has a light taste.

28
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:21,920
Well said.

29
00:03:23,739 --> 00:03:24,709
Dr. Zhang.

30
00:03:24,905 --> 00:03:28,619
The steamed cake and durian cheese roll
is not a matter of life and death.

31
00:03:28,826 --> 00:03:30,120
Why do you get into a dilemma?

32
00:03:30,161 --> 00:03:31,611
I'm not in a dilemma.

33
00:03:32,806 --> 00:03:36,000
By the way,
Dr. Zhang, I need your signature.

34
00:03:42,684 --> 00:03:44,346
Patient number nine
doesn't require blood transfusion anymore.

35
00:03:44,387 --> 00:03:45,268
Sure, Dr. Zhang.

36
00:03:45,455 --> 00:03:47,039
Give him some liquid and IV fluids.

37
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,905
Conduct complete blood count
on him tomorrow morning.

38
00:03:48,946 --> 00:03:49,802
Sure.

39
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,080
Okay.

40
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:53,480
Thank you, Dr. Zhang.

41
00:03:55,096 --> 00:03:56,526
The pen belongs to me.

42
00:03:56,616 --> 00:03:58,040
It's the last pen I have.

43
00:03:58,546 --> 00:03:59,440
I'm sorry.

44
00:04:02,976 --> 00:04:03,960
Goodbye, Dr. Zhang.

45
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:10,440
I bet you're hungry. Take it.

46
00:04:13,814 --> 00:04:15,561
It looks like you're a practical person.

47
00:04:16,230 --> 00:04:18,000
I tried cheese before.

48
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,360
It's too sweet and I'm bored of it.

49
00:04:21,244 --> 00:04:22,600
As I age,

50
00:04:23,096 --> 00:04:26,400
I find that I prefer a lighter taste.

51
00:04:29,376 --> 00:04:30,760
I won't be shy then!

52
00:04:45,336 --> 00:04:49,146
Liang Mu Ze, do you prefer steamed cake
or durian cheese roll?

53
00:05:25,031 --> 00:05:27,201
Don't forget to take a rest at work.

54
00:05:29,595 --> 00:05:30,964
Don't worry, Ms. Lan.

55
00:05:31,005 --> 00:05:33,680
I'm a woman who aspires
to conquer the world with a scalpel.

56
00:05:49,734 --> 00:05:54,354
(Liang Mu Ze, do you prefer steamed cake
or durian cheese roll?)

57
00:06:04,058 --> 00:06:07,398
(Vitalik)

58
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:07,720
Go!

59
00:08:06,326 --> 00:08:07,199
It's quite good.

60
00:08:08,302 --> 00:08:09,320
It's perfect.

61
00:08:10,606 --> 00:08:11,566
All right.

62
00:08:11,672 --> 00:08:13,520
The surgery is a success.
Thank you for the hard work, everyone.

63
00:08:14,176 --> 00:08:15,243
You've worked hard, Dr. Zhang.

64
00:08:15,902 --> 00:08:16,799
I'll leave the rest to you.

65
00:08:33,404 --> 00:08:36,424
Just now, the patient
received cardiac tamponade treatment.

66
00:08:36,465 --> 00:08:38,821
What are the issues should we take note of
in the coming treatment?

67
00:08:38,862 --> 00:08:40,000
Anti-shock therapy,

68
00:08:40,336 --> 00:08:41,424
blood transfusion, intravenous drip,

69
00:08:41,465 --> 00:08:42,918
tranquillizing, analgesic, oxygen intake,

70
00:08:42,959 --> 00:08:44,889
pericardiocentesis
and pericardial drainage.

71
00:08:44,976 --> 00:08:46,176
If none of the above works,

72
00:08:46,217 --> 00:08:48,225
and if the pericardium
continues to bleed,

73
00:08:48,266 --> 00:08:50,280
exploratory thoracotomy
needs to be conducted immediately.

74
00:08:50,856 --> 00:08:51,720
What else?

75
00:08:53,013 --> 00:08:54,560
Use antibiotics to prevent infection.

76
00:09:09,129 --> 00:09:10,560
Go.

77
00:09:11,989 --> 00:09:13,640
One, two, three. Go!

78
00:09:25,786 --> 00:09:27,160
Go!

79
00:10:16,256 --> 00:10:17,280
Unlock the security!

80
00:10:21,726 --> 00:10:22,698
Shoot when you're ready!

81
00:10:32,449 --> 00:10:33,880
Go!

82
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:40,655
You two.

83
00:10:40,696 --> 00:10:41,720
Shoot when you're ready!

84
00:10:41,761 --> 00:10:43,240
-Wolf, go!
-Yes!

85
00:10:47,302 --> 00:10:48,160
Hurry up!

86
00:10:50,223 --> 00:10:51,200
Unlock the security!

87
00:10:52,431 --> 00:10:53,741
Pay attention to the rear left.

88
00:10:53,782 --> 00:10:54,800
Shoot when you're ready!

89
00:10:58,880 --> 00:10:59,725
It hit the target. Let's go!

90
00:10:59,766 --> 00:11:00,976
Let's go!

91
00:11:01,626 --> 00:11:02,600
Let's go!

92
